          "text": " is a scalar function in Microsoft SQL Server. It is designed to retrieve a specific value, referred to as the \"Therm Factor,\" from an account table. This function is used to calculate or retrieve a conversion factor related to energy consumption, specifically for accounts associated with Con Edison, a utility company."
